<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> matsyānvavāyapāthōdhipravṛddhikaracaṁdramāḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Āsī
<lb n="2" break="no"/>darjunabhūpālō maṁḍalēśvarabhūbhujāṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> Agraṇīstasya tanayō
<lb n="3"/>jayaṁtasamavikramaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> vijayaśrīsakhaśrīmā<unclear>ṁ ja</unclear>yaṁtadharaṇī
<lb n="4" break="no"/>patiḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">2</supplied> bhimādēvīti vikhyātā dēvī tasya mahīpatēḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> vahaṁtī nṛharēraṁ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ghrau bhaktiṁ mālāsamarppaṇē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">3</supplied> ravisiṁddhuviyatsaṁkhvāgaṇitē śakavatsa
<lb n="6" break="no"/>rē mārggaśuklatrayōdasyāyuktagiṣpativāsarē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">4</supplied> gōpālanāyakasutā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>t bṛṁdāvana Iti śṛtāt <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Aṣṭabhirddaśabhirnniṣkairdhṛtvā prasthapramāṇitaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">5</supplied> pu
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṣpārāmaṁ caturnniṣkaiḥ krītvā tassyaiva hastakē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> stiraṁ dhṛtavatī mālāṁ
<lb n="9"/>nṛharēḥ prativāsaraṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">6</supplied> pravarttatāmayaṁ dharmō yāvadācaṁdra
<lb n="10" break="no"/>tārakaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śakavarṣaṁbulu 1270 gunēṇṭi mārggaśīrṣa śukla trayō
<lb n="11" break="no"/>daśiyu bṛhaspativāramunāṁḍu Oḍḍavādi śrīmammahāma
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ṁḍalēśa jayaṁtarājula mahādēvi bhīmādēvi svābhimataphalasi
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ddhigānu gōpālanāyaku koḍkucēta ma 18 ṇṭiki prasādakuṁcālu 2 ṭhā
<lb n="14" break="no"/>vupaṭṭi vīracētana tōṁṭa koni nityamunnu Ayidu mūḷlu tiru
<lb n="15" break="no"/>māla narasiṁhanāthuniki cātiṁpa <unclear>peṭṭiṁci</unclear> Ī prasādamu vīru koni
<lb n="16"/>tirumāla cātagalāru <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī dharmmu śrīvaiṣṇava <unclear>ra</unclear>kṣa <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

